  <div data-component="article-content">


            <p>Stuntman Hollywood - an explosive return for the beloved racing series - has been revealed at tonight's State of Play livestream.
</p>
<p>An arcade racer, Stuntman Hollywood features many cars from a variety of movies new and old. These include cars from The Fast and Furious, Back to the Future, Nightrider, and more.
</p>

<figure>
<p>
<a aria-label="Stuntman: Hollywood - Announce Trailer | PS5 Games" data-platform="youtube" href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/A7NZpeAmdxk?autoplay=1" onclick="((e) => { e.preventDefault(); e.currentTarget.closest('.video_wrapper').innerHTML = e.currentTarget.querySelector('template').innerHTML; enableElements(); })(event)" title="Click to play video from YouTube">
